originalText: I've been informed of your refusal to accomplish the given assignments. That concludes our cooperation. Goodbye, $(context.player.Name).
Maybe I should order another drink...
Haven't seen you around here before. You stuck in this hole now as well?

originalText: Hmm? I'm sorry, I don't have time to chat, I'm waiting for someone.
$(context.player.Name), I've waited for you for quite some time back there, yet you never showed up. I'm sorry, but I had to move on. I had some business I needed to attend to.
I told you we'd meet again, $(context.player.Name). You look well enough. Listen, I'd love to chat, but I'm waiting for someone important, I'll catch you later.
Oh, $(context.player.Name), there's a familiar face. I'd love to chat with you at the moment, but I'm waiting for someone important. I'll catch you later.

So you are $(context.player.Name). Name's Jack Quicksilver. Abram told me you come from SGS. I was stuck there recently, it's funny how we never met. But, that's not important right now. He also told me you helped him in Junkyard. Told me you have potential.
...And here $(#he/she) is. You've talked to Abram, I presume. He informed me earlier you helped him in Junkyard. Told me you have potential.
Well, well, if it isn't $(context.player.Name). I told you we would meet again. Abram informed me you helped him in Junkyard. Told me you have potential.
Well, well, if it isn't $(context.player.Name). We talked briefly at SGS, yet here we are again. Interesting. Abram informed me you helped him in Junkyard. Told me you have potential.
